metadata.name: WaGeMi & Me!
metadata.description:
Little Cemprut is so happy surrounded by some new friends that accompany her journey to Nifty Land🙋🏻‍♀️💕 Let her introduce to you:

Wati📜
The geek one, the one who who share knowledge about the road map, the utility, and the technical things to ride along the journey 💕

Gendhis🐟
The friendly one, who’s always introduce her with all of her friends & relatives. No need to feel alone in a Nifty Land, she always have a friends to call for help & support🐟🐬🐳🐋

Midah💐
The currator🌷 She have an eyes & taste to look at all things surrounded. She always gives some constructive inputs & shares a lot of fresh ideas 🌸

Little Cemprut & Cemeng are so glad to this new kind of friendship to ride along this new journey 🙏🏻🥰🙋🏻‍♀️💕

Craft On !!!

Manual Paper Cutting + Digital Illustration
3000 x 3000 px
